8 driving a commercial motor vehicle that'complies with
9 minimum federal standards established by federal
10 regulation enumerated in title 49 Code of Federal
11 Regulations, part 383, subparts G and H;
12 (3) [Haa Ha-waii as the state of domicile as defined in
